</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDBE937FFB1C83BFF47FDAFFB4521F1" blockId="11.[136,1452,554,1012]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">
This taxon was renamed within 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFE27FDAEFDC4214D" box="[488,639,554,580]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="glaucinum">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFE27FDAEFDC4214D" box="[488,639,554,580]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">H. glaucinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF594C6FFB1C83BFD4AFDAFFCF2214D" author="Jordan, A." box="[645,841,554,580]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" refId="ref7843" refString="Jordan, A. (1848) Catalogue des Graines recoltees au Jardin botanique de la Ville de Dijon en 1848, offertes en echange. Dijon (Divionensis), 22 pp." type="book" year="1848">
<collectingCountry id="F373A9A7FFB1C83BFD4AFDAFFD6B214D" box="[645,720,554,580]" name="Jordan" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">Jordan</collectingCountry>
(1848: 22)
</bibRefCitation>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF594C6FFB1C83BFCBFFDAFFB1A214C" author="Bolos, O. de &amp; Vigo, J." box="[880,1185,554,581]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" refId="ref6486" refString="Bolos, O. de &amp; Vigo, J. (1996) Flora dels Paisos Catalans 3 (Pirolacies-Compostes). Barcino, Barcelona, 1230 pp." type="book" year="1996">Bolòs &amp; Vigo (1996: 1054)</bibRefCitation>
, as 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFB07FDAEFD2A2161" authority="(Freyn ex Zahn) O. Bolos &amp; Vigo" authorityName="O. Bolos &amp; Vigo" authorityYear="1995" baseAuthorityName="Freyn ex Zahn" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="glaucinum" subSpecies="brachypus">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFB07FDAEFAE4214D" box="[1224,1375,554,580]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">H. glaucinum</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFF47FDCBFF462161" box="[136,253,590,616]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">brachypus</emphasis>
(Freyn ex Zahn) O. Bolòs &amp; Vigo
</taxonomicName>
, based on the cited basionym 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFC3FFDCAFF7F2185" authority="Freyn ex Zahn" authorityName="Zahn" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="praecox" subSpecies="brachypus">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFC3FFDCAFBD52161" box="[1008,1134,591,616]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">H. praecox</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFB07FDCBFA862161" box="[1224,1341,590,616]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">brachypus</emphasis>
Freyn ex Zahn
</taxonomicName>
, in Engler, Pflanzenreich 75 (
<collectionCode id="ED7571F2FFB1C83BFDDBFDF7FD882185" box="[532,563,626,652]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">IV</collectionCode>
. 280): 240. 1921. However, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF594C6FFB1C83BFCBAFDF7FB9B2184" author="Greuter, W." box="[885,1056,626,653]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" refId="ref7577" refString="Greuter, W. (2006) Compositae (pro parte majore). In: Greuter, W. &amp; Raab-Straube, E. von (Ed.) Compositae. Euro + Med Plantbase - the information resource for Euro-Mediterranean plant diversity. Available from: http: // ww 2. bgbm. org / EuroPlusMed / PTaxonDetail. asp? NameId = 7707446 &amp; PTRefFk = 7000000 (accessed 6 January 2021)" type="url" year="2006">Greuter (2006)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF594C6FFB1C83BFBE3FDF7FA902185" author="Gottschlich, G." box="[1068,1323,626,652]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" pagination="5 - 416" refId="ref7467" refString="Gottschlich, G. (2007) Die Gattung Hieracium L. (Compositae) im Herbarium Rupert Huter (Vinzentinum Brixen, BRIX). Kommentiertes Verzeichnis mit taxonomischen und nomenklatorischen Erganzungen unter besonderer Berucksichtigung der Typus-Belege. Veroffentlichungen des Tiroler Landesmuseums Ferdinandeum 86 (Sonderband): 5 - 416." type="book chapter" year="2007">Gottschlich (2007: 34)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF594C6FFB1C83BFAABFDF7FE8721B9" author="Mateo, G. &amp; Egido, F." pageId="11" pageNumber="212" refId="ref8422" refString="Mateo, G. &amp; Egido, F. del (2017) Estudio monografico de los generos Hieracium y Pilosella en Espana. Con referencias a Portugal y los Pirineos franceses. Monografias de Botanica Iberica, nº 20, Jolube, Jaca, 422 pp." type="book" year="2017">Mateo &amp; Egido (2017)</bibRefCitation>
consider the correct basionym the name distributed by 
<collectionCode id="ED7571F2FFB1C83BFC7AFD13FC7E21B9" box="[949,965,662,688]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFC1EFD13FBB721B9" authority="G. Rigo" authorityName="G. Rigo" box="[977,1036,662,688]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyparochromidae" genus="Porta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Porta</taxonomicName>
and 
<collectionCode id="ED7571F2FFB1C83BFB8AFD13FBE721B9" box="[1093,1116,662,688]" country="Switzerland" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15706" name="Conservatoire et Jardin botaniques de la Ville de Genève" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" type="Herbarium">G</collectionCode>
. Rigo in the exsiccatum “ 
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFA44FD13FEE921DD" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">Pl. Balear. Exs. 1885</emphasis>
” (without number). On the original label of the sheet the diagnosis given by Freyn is very short (“ 
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFF51FD5BFC8921F1" box="[158,818,734,760]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">calathiis mediocribus aggregatis ramulo subaequilongibus</emphasis>
”) and certainly of poor diagnostic value.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDBE937FFB1C83BFF47FC87FBA620A5" blockId="11.[136,1452,554,1012]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">
Moreover, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF594C6FFB1C83BFECBFC87FE712015" author="Zahn, K. H." box="[260,458,770,796]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" pagination="1 - 1146" refId="ref9586" refString="Zahn, K. H. (1921 - 1923) Hieracium. In: Engler, A. (Ed.) Das Pflanzenreich. Regni vegetabilis conspectus, 75 - 82 (IV, 280) [pars Compositae - Hieracium]. Wilhelm Engelmann, Leipzig, pp. 1 - 1146." type="book chapter" year="1921">Zahn (1921: 420)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFD93FC86FD622015" box="[604,729,770,796]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="praecox">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFD93FC86FDCB2015" box="[604,624,771,796]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFDB0FC86FD622015" box="[639,729,771,796]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">praecox</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[…] 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFCD8FC87FB982015" authority="Freyn" authorityName="Freyn" box="[791,1059,770,796]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="praecox" subSpecies="brachypus">
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFCAAFC87FC612015" box="[869,986,770,796]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">brachypus</emphasis>
Freyn
</taxonomicName>
in litt. ad Huter (1886) pro var. 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFA5FFC86FF4E2049" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="praecocis">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFA5FFC86FF4E2049" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">H. praecocis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”. He was apparently unaware of the fact that 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFD39FCA3FC8A2049" authority="G. Rigo" authorityName="G. Rigo" box="[758,817,806,832]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyparochromidae" genus="Porta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Porta</taxonomicName>
and Rigo, and not Huter, were those who distributed the exsiccata. The 
<typeStatus id="54DF5795FFB1C83BFEE2FCCFFEE6206D" box="[301,349,842,868]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">type</typeStatus>
locality given by Zahn, “ 
<collectingRegion id="49A027D5FFB1C83BFDBAFCCFFD64206D" box="[629,735,842,868]" country="Spain" name="Illes Baleares" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">Balearen</collectingRegion>
: Puig mayor de Torrella, 
<quantity id="4C9C44D2FFB1C83BFC39FCCFFB2F206D" box="[1014,1172,842,868]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="1.1" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" unit="m" value="1200.0" valueMax="1300.0" valueMin="1100.0">1100–1300 m</quantity>
”, is a shortened and fully compatible provenance to that given by 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFD87FCEBFD382081" authority="G. Rigo" authorityName="G. Rigo" box="[584,643,878,904]" class="Insecta" family="Rhyparochromidae" genus="Porta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Porta</taxonomicName>
and Rigo (“Balarium insula Majore: ad rupes umbros. de Puig Major de Torella, sol. calcar., 
<quantity id="4C9C44D2FFB1C83BFEA5FC17FDBE20A5" box="[362,517,914,940]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="1.1" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" unit="m" value="1200.0" valueMax="1300.0" valueMin="1100.0">1100–1300 m</quantity>
) and most likely he refers to the same exsiccata
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDBE937FFB1C83BFF72FC30FB2320FD" blockId="11.[136,1452,554,1012]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFF72FC30FE1520D9" bold="true" box="[189,430,949,976]" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">Taxonomic remarks</emphasis>
:—The examination of the isolectotype clearly shows that this plant is conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFA5FFC32FEA620FD" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="majoricanum">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFA5FFC32FEA620FD" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">H. majoricanum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The presence of 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB1C83BFE2AFC5EFDC620FD" box="[485,637,986,1012]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="11" pageNumber="212" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="glaucinum">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFB1C83BFE2AFC5EFDC620FD" box="[485,637,986,1012]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="212">H. glaucinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the Balearic archipelago should be excluded.
</paragraph>
